      <p id="Par43">Consider now dataset V with one character state (A) changing to another (G) in just one taxon (N), but retaining <italic>n</italic> taxa and <italic>p</italic> positions. Denoting the changed frequencies for A and G with a star we can apply Eq. <xref rid="Equ11" ref-type="disp-formula">11</xref> here:<disp-formula id="Equ12"><label>12</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M39">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
